<section class="text-flow">

  <h2>Which properties benefit most</h2>

  <p>
    A post-storm inspection is especially useful for properties where location, outdoor areas or long vacancy periods increase the risk of visible changes after severe weather.
  </p>

  <h3>Typical examples</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>villas in exposed locations</li>
    <li>high-end apartments with sea views</li>
    <li>second homes with extended absence periods</li>
    <li>residences with large terraces and garden areas</li>
    <li>properties with pool surroundings and sensitive outdoor structures</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    The service is equally valuable shortly before an arrival, when the property should not only be checked, but also restored to a reliable and well-ordered condition if necessary.
  </p>

